Requirements -
===========

1. User should be able to register
2. User should be able to add contacts / block contacts / unblock contacts
3. User should be able to import contacts
4. User should be able to mark calss as spam
5. User should get notified if a call is spam if he gets the call
6. User should be able to search by name/phone number
7. User should be able to upgrade to premium plan
8. User's contact should get stored in global directory once he signs up

